```
# Rust-specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock

# Dependencies
vendor/

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Python caches (if any Python files exist in project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.so

# Build outputs
dist/
build/
*.out
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.a
*.dylib

# Testing
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.nyc_output/
istanbul/
```